  this bill has been brought with a view to bringing about improvement in the society and to take care of the mental  health  of  human  being      with  the  advancement  of  the  world  and  the disintegration of the social structure mental tension is surging high  i would like to say that when human beings get individualistic then they hardly share their pain   pleasure  with  other  persons    unambiguous  provisions  have  not  been  made regarding the rehabilitation of the patients in this bill  providing employment to people should also be laid stress because unemployment is also one of the reasons of mental tension   at the same time better facilities for the treatment  of mental patients should be provided in the hospitals        